index.title: To The Ocean with The Son #15
index.description: The most longest and durable ride with my son on this moment to the ocean coast near by Santa Cruz. We got a tent and took overnight on the coast.

index.title: San Francisco to Los Angeles, Day 6 of 6 #14
index.description: Unfortunately afternoon my wife caught me in Oxnard a little before Los Angeles but I swear that I would get Malibu before sunset if would have more time
